				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Ceramic Skull and Ceramic gavel can both be ignored if you use tribute...same is true for BA4.
<br />

<br />
As for your gear, I don't see any glaring problems...simply look for items that have more HP...that should be your main focus for now.
<br />

<br />
Without knowing the market on The Rathe, it's hard to give any more specific advice than that...<br />_________________<br /><img src="http://home.comcast.net/~topknot/wsb/media/350795/site1015.jpg" border="0" />
