<br />

<br />
AE adds 25% to your mana pool. While I'm not downplaying the benefit AH has to aggro kiting, (it's important), AE is far more important. You can substitute SOW potions (or Jboots or run3) plus Spell Haste to make up for a lack of AH, but nothing you have will make up for AE and saving 25% of your mana costs. 
<br />

<br />

<br />
Also: hold off on skull &amp; gavel purchases. They have a required level 46 on'em, iirc. 
